quran[7{c,v,t}:
29,39,aur qaroon aur firaon aur Haman ko bhi ( halaak kar diya ) aur unn ke paas moose khuli nishani le kar aeye to woh malik mein maghrour hogaye aur hamaray qaboo se nikal jaane walay nah they
29,40,to hum ne sab ko unn ke gunaaho ke sabab pakar liya. so un mein kuch to aisay they jin par hum ne patharon kameinhہ barsaya. aur kuch aisay they jin ko chngharh ne aapkrha aur kuch aisay they jin ko hum ne zameen mein dhansa diya. aur kuch aisay they jin ko ghark kar diya aur khuda aisa nah tha ke unn par zulm karta lekin wohi apne aap par zulm karte they
29,41,jin logon ne khuda ke siwa ( ouron ko ) karsaaz bana rakha hai unn ki misaal makri ki si hai ke woh bhi aik ( terhan ka ) ghar banati hai. aur kuch shak nahi ke tamam gharon se kamzor makri ka ghar hai kash yeh ( is baat ko ) jantay
29,42,yeh jis cheez ko khuda ke siwa pkarte hain ( khuwa ) woh kuch hi ho khuda ussay jaanta hai. aur woh ghalib aur hikmat wala hai
29,43,aur yeh misalein hum logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye bayan karte hain aur ussay to ehley Danish hi samajte hain
29,44,khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko hikmat ke sath pedakiya hai. kuch shak nahi ke imaan walon ke liye is mein nishani hai
29,45,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! yeh ) kitaab jo tumhari taraf wahi ki gayi hai is ko parha karo aur namaz ke paband raho. kuch shak nahi ke namaz be hiyai aur buri baton se rokti hai. aur khuda ka zikar bara ( acha kaam ) hai. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda ussay jaanta hai
